    "However, the data-driven approaches applied for the tasks of spatial predictions assume independence among observations.",
    "If SAC is not properly addressed, the geospatial analysis may result in misleading conclusions and erroneous inferences.",
    "Consequently, the significance of research findings may be overestimated, potentially affecting the validity and reliability of predictions 7, 99.",
